    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"liberal myth\"? That's a pretty strong way to put it. Aren't there legitimate concerns that if we start making constant exceptions for religious groups, we're basically creating a two-tier system of citizenship where some people don't have to follow the same laws as everyone else? Wouldn't that eventually just erode the principle of equality before the law?",
